Classical swine fever, Russia
------------------------------
Information received on 15 Feb 2010 from Dr Nicolay Vlasov, CVO,
Veterinary services, Ministry of Agriculture and Food, Moscow, Russia

Summary
Report type: Immediate notification
Start date 23 Jan 2010
Date of 1st confirmation of the event 8 Feb 2010
Report date 15 Feb 2010
Date submitted to OIE 15 Feb 2010
Reason for notification: Reoccurrence of a listed disease
Date of previous occurrence 15 Jan 2010
Manifestation of disease: Clinical disease
Causal agent: Classical swine fever virus
Nature of diagnosis: Clinical, Laboratory (advanced)
This event pertains to a defined zone within the country

New outbreaks
Outbreak 1 Mityahinskoe hunting unit, Rudnianskiy, Volgogradskaya Oblast
Date of start of the outbreak 23 Jan 2010
Outbreak status: Continuing (or date resolved not provided)
Epidemiological unit: Not applicable
